44
00:04:27,833 --> 00:04:29,130
Push.

45
00:04:39,711 --> 00:04:41,440
God, he's beautiful.

46
00:04:47,452 --> 00:04:50,353
- He's beautiful.
- I wanna hold him. I wanna see him.

47
00:04:50,522 --> 00:04:54,322
We'll clean him up first,
and then he's all yours.

48
00:05:01,333 --> 00:05:02,823
Doctor?

49
