00:09:38,209 --> 00:09:40,268
<i>Please stay off the</i> h...

82
00:09:50,255 --> 00:09:51,620
<i>Dr. Henry?</i>

83
00:09:59,864 --> 00:10:01,798
Dr. Henry?

84
00:10:06,571 --> 00:10:09,472
